<script type="text/javascript">
function togPhase(n) {
	var e = document.getElementById('phasehint' + n);
	e.style.display = e.style.display == 'none' ? 'block' : 'none';
}
function togAllPhases(display) {
	for (var i = 1; i <= 50; i++) {
		var e = document.getElementById('phasehint' + i);
		if (!e) break;
		e.style.display = display;
	}
}
function addHint(n) {
	var e = document.getElementById('phase');
	for (var i = 0; i < e.childNodes.length; i++) {
		e.childNodes[i].selected = e.childNodes[i].value == n ? 'selected' : '';
	}
	e = document.getElementById('text');
	e.focus();
	e.select();
}
</script>

<div class="mm white">
This quest  is called '<span class="yellow">Under the Sea!</span>',<br/>
for Adventurers levels <span class="yellow">140</span> to <span class="yellow">180</span>.<br />


<span class="hg"><a href="/npc/255">Lord Vendredi</a> [<a href="/area/51">Sigil</a>] is the master in charge of this quest.</span><br />

I have heard tales of a fantastic underwater city called Atlantis, far to<br />
the southeast.  They say it is inhabited by merfolk, wonderful creatures who<br />
are reportedly half-man, half-fish, and able to breathe underwater.  Since I<br />
am unable to make the journey myself at this time due to other pressing<br />
matters, please go in my stead and learn more about this unique city and its<br />
citizens.  Don't forget to stop by the palace, and pay a visit to the<br />
Avatar, the only human who supposedly resides permanently in that lost city.<br />
Your efforts on my behalf will be well rewarded indeed!<br />

<span class="hy">Upon successful completion of this quest you can receive:</span><br />

<span class="hm">*</span>Up to <span class="yellow">75</span> quest points, <span class="yellow">8</span> practice points, <span class="yellow">40,000</span> experience points,<br/>
&nbsp;<span class="yellow">0</span> build points, <span class="yellow">0</span> piety, and <span class="yellow">12,000</span> gold pieces.<br />


You have <span class="yellow">400</span> minutes remaining to complete this quest.<br />

Under the Sea! consists of:<br />


	<div class="phase" id="phase1">


		<a class="hints" href="javascript:togPhase(1);">Phase 1</a>: Visit <a href="/npc/2719">An Atlantian merman</a>. 		
		<div class="phasehints" id="phasehint1" style="display: none;">

<div class="phaseinfomob">in <a href="/area/2">Atlantis</a>.</div>


			<div class="phasehint">
				Wonders around Atlantis.				&mdash;
				Vur							</div>


		</div>
	</div>


	<div class="phase" id="phase2">


		<a class="hints" href="javascript:togPhase(2);">Phase 2</a>: Journey to <a href="/room/22936">Gathered Goods &amp; Curiosities</a>. 		
		<div class="phasehints" id="phasehint2" style="display: none;">

<div class="phaseinforoom">in <a href="/area/2">Atlantis</a>.</div>


			<div class="phasehint">
				Six north of the down into Atlantis.				&mdash;
				Vur							</div>


		</div>
	</div>


	<div class="phase" id="phase3">


