<div class="phaseinfoitem">from <a href="/npc/5833">Marie the magic shop owner</a> (shop #11) [<a href="/room/29943/">Marie's Shop of Wonders</a>, <a href="/area/140" class="white">Aequtus</a>],<br /><a href="/npc/2716">Marie the magic shop owner</a> (shop #11) [<a href="/room/25093/">Marie's Shop of Wonders</a>, <a href="/area/2" class="white">Atlantis</a>].</div>


			<div class="phasehint">
				Enter the mirror in Eiram's Shop of Wonders and you will enter a new shop called Marie's Shop of Wonders. They are sold there.				&mdash;
